{"tid":1521902,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"19文妓-陶傑：「殺光香港人」 ？ chinazi 屠殺香港人 計劃 進化？","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:39:19.000Z","uid":242537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d1cda00c783e810e3d8ccbb82fbdba2c076e214c","tid":1521902,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"香港六月風暴，親中陣營和警方稱黑衣示威人士為「曱甴」，也就是蟑螂，被指為散播仇恨言論。危機深化，大陸網民有稱要殺光香港狗。 <br />\n<br />\n喧罵鋪天蓋地，若有一日戒嚴而軍隊接管香港，輕則「二二八」事件重演香港版，因有「香港民族論」之出版，億萬大陸網民認為香港人人想港獨。巨大「民意」支持，不止「六四」，一旦美中大戰逼近，大陸民族危機加劇，已經煽動得差不多，香港將來發生「滅族（Genocide）、即「殺光香港人」的風險，正在增加。 <br />\n<br />\n全文： <a href=\"http://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/0831/1336631.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2019%2F0831%2F1336631.html&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4Wh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=7dc2ba4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/0831/1336631.html</a>"},{"pid":"c338de191052b3b56caa4b80238a64012920ae73","tid":1521902,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span>"},{"pid":"c7a632aa0005957f7b7e19e652fedfd7eae2863a","tid":1521902,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"明居正「透視中國」：香港局勢推演：中共如何平息事態<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A-YqFc9CNa0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA-YqFc9CNa0&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4Wh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=2b7196c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A-YqFc9CNa0</a>"},{"pid":"b75d18eebc74918ae543c8944618ccf3f6a8afc0","tid":1521902,"uid":202577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"為咗維穩，中共只能夠大力鼓吹民族主義<br />\n無乜第二個方法"},{"pid":"3647e22279139c605762b08cc97ea96ac733befb","tid":1521902,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"民族主義對於被壓迫窮苦既人吹唔起"},{"pid":"381ae9bc8ea515923527fb0095d9e03fe2582c9a","tid":1521902,"uid":34334,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:40:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48ae9d23f8d3b00f3cea613fdaae2fb568e7f4ac","tid":1521902,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"推上國際 香港正深陷人道危機"},{"pid":"8caf42869abca37efd431fde2835c11a53929b6a","tid":1521902,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e603379e7a540b82595a2802aab60efbe02cbfcd","tid":1521902,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"